     H            Y.
     F** EDTR02A****************************************
     F*  EDIT USER PART WITH HYPHEN                    *
     F*  J.WATANABE    2021.05.04                      *
     F*------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'EDTR02A'
     F*                    PARM           $MHIN  20
     F*                    PARM           $MHIN2 23
     F*  IN  $MHIN : 20A USER PART#
     F*  OUT $MHIN2: 23A USER PART# WITH HYPHEN
     F**************************************************
     I            DS
     I                                        1  20 @1MHIN
     I                                        1   5 @1MHN1
     I                                        6  10 @1MHN2
     I                                       11  15 @1MHN3
     I                                       16  20 @1MHN4
     I            DS
     I                                        1  23 @2MHIN
     I                                        1   5 @2MHN1
     I                                        6   6 @2HF1
     I                                        7  11 @2MHN2
     I                                       12  12 @2HF2
     I                                       13  17 @2MHN3
     I                                       18  18 @2HF3
     I                                       19  23 @2MHN4
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $MHIN  20
     C                     PARM           $MHIN2 23
      *
     C                     MOVEL$MHIN     @1MHIN
      *
     C                     MOVEL@1MHN1    @2MHN1
     C                     MOVEL@1MHN2    @2MHN2
     C                     MOVEL@1MHN3    @2MHN3
      *
     C           @1MHN2    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE ' '       @2HF1
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE '-'       @2HF1
     C                     END
      *
     C           @1MHN3    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE ' '       @2HF2
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE '-'       @2HF2
     C                     END
      *
     C           @1MHN4    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE ' '       @2HF3
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE '-'       @2HF3
     C                     END
      *
     C                     MOVEL@2MHIN    $MHIN2
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
